Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:53.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:57.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We're both pros, Touya. What do you think of me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya, I'm..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him? He didn't have to ignore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, he pisses me off. Just because he's doing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's not just doing 'well'...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't just catch up to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these are the pairings for the Ooteai matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru... there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My first opponent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tou...ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My first opponent is... Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He called,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's big news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's in an ambulance, on the way to the hospital, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:18.80,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs28}Fifty-third match\N\N{\fs}The Confession of Sai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The man closest to the divine move...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, let us play an even match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I really get a chance to play him in an even match?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And, where's the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's all right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's still at the hospital though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go check up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.65,Note,,0,0,0,,{\move(320,46,320,71)\frz-4.5\fs40\t(\fs35)\fscx160\1a&HFF&\3c&HFF&}AISHINDOU HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we there? They told you to go here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Go institute told me that it was here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,could you tell me where the inpatients are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What department is he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai, what department?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the name of the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin! The Go player.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He was brought here three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared to death when I heard that you were hospitalized because of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that your alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working too hard, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for worrying you, Hirose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just me. Everyone at the Go salon was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire store was in a panic when your wife told us what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bigger issue than a Go salon panicking, Ichikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tension ran through the Go world that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened the day before the third game of the Jyudan match, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata, what did you do as the challenger, when you heard that Master Touya collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All affiliates and I headed to Ehime, where the match was supposed to take place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With the understanding that they would notify us of his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We were worried about him, but still there was a chance that we would still play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for Master Touya in front of the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,until his loss by default was decided on the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have been there if it was closer, around Shizuoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself, when I woke up and looked at the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, please don't be so reckless with your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth game is in five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,, Master, will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, though the doctors do not seem to approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what an incredible room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we be going, Ichikawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not staying long. I just came to see how Master Touya was doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:58.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't tell them that Sai kept bugging me to come check up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata, there's no need to say that. He came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll go get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pro as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I work the counter at the Go salon you played Akira-kun at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.92,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(108,62)}{\fs28\b1\1c&H00&\3a&HFF&\1a&H80&}{\fad(400,0)}{\fscx50\fscy75}Domestic and International travel\N{\fscx115}Sky Blue Travel{\fscx54\fscy75}\NTours of various locales - Rental
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.92,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(125,280)}{\fs30\b1\1c&H00&\3a&HFF&}{\fad(400,0)}{\fscx148}Go Salon\N{\fscx60\fscy70}Weekdays 1PM~10PM\NWeekends 12PM~9PM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.92,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(150,460)}{\fs25\b1\1c&H00&\3a&HFF&\1a&H80&}{\fad(400,0)}{\fscx220\fscy90}6F\N{\fscx80\fscy75}Hair Studio\N{\fscx220\fscy90}JOY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time at any Go salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.  Write your name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's another kid here. Can I play him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You beat Akira-kun back then. It's no wonder that you became a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to have seen that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun refuses to show it to me, and none of the customers remembers it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither Master Touya nor Mr. Ogata know about that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I played that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'd be in trouble if they knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I heard that you collapsed from a heart attack at the Go Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they want me to stay here for another ten days or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, why don't you relax here for a month or so, instead of only ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You can go to matches directly from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can play as much Go as you'd like even here. Right, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I set it up yesterday, with permission from the head of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If he learns how to play Go over the Internet, the master won't be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, Master Touya is going to learn about computers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, he only taught me how to play Go on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so even Master Touya is going to play Go over the internet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're playing internet Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't hard to learn how to play Go on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing Go is what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san, maybe we should get going soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, shall I take these gifts to your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I drove.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ichikawa-san is going to Master Touya's house, I'll drive you back, Hirose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Shindou-kun plays Go on the internet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounded interested, but what do you mean by 'after all'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirose-san saw him at an internet cafe along time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw him from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to the Go salon afterwards and told us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun was there, too, and stormed out as soon as he found out where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly was running quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And did Akira-kun meet Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun didn't say anything about it when he got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was summer two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun was in the store during the day, so it had to be during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, it was around the end of summer vacation two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:23.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Summer two years ago... Internet Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's around the time when Akira-kun played Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun stormed out of the store when he learned that Shindou was playing at an internet cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:37.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Did he think that Shindou was Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:44.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Or did he think there was some connection between Sai and Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming. Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I collapse on the day you were supposed to play Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Akira didn't go to the match because he didn't think he could play calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably worried him quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You play Go on the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably wouldn't have had to learn it if I weren't in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just started yesterday, but I played Akira this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that I can play even while I'm in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but I miss the feel of the Go stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a stopgap while I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only while you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't play Go on the internet, but I have a friend who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to play you, Master Touya, very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His nick on the internet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-kun showed me the match Akira played against Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way for black to live in the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,About Sai and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai has... he has always wanted to play you, Master Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But he only plays Go on the internet, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he hiding behind the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His name...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't plan on telling me his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a pro, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's common for a good player to wish that he could play a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it displeases me that he wants to keep his identity a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him here. I'll play him any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But not on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I messed up... sorry, Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us a board and stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen the match Sai played against Touya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how strong Sai is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He is very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But Akira lost that game because he could not read deeply enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't know exactly how strong he is until I play him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then play him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if its just once, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On the internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He can only play on the internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It will provide a nice distraction during the Jyudan match games.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:22.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The Sai that everyone was excited over on the internet two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Something about someone really strong being on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His nick is Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His Tesuji and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he played like Shuusaku, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Honinbou Shuusaku!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I replay Shuusaku's matches all the time, and I thought they were similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I watched him play a few more times after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He became stronger with every game. His game is changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As if ... Shuusaku learned modern Joseki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:15.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It is true that I thought of Shindou, when I heard that he might be a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:25.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The game that Shindou played during the Wakajishisen, wasn't one of Sai's games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou is not Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then who is Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:36.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A fake one showed up quite a while ago, but he quickly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:40.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The real Sai is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in anyone who refuses to reveal himself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:54.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Where is he right now? Is he no longer on the net?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A distraction, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai, it is a chance to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But please keep it a secret that I know Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell others about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But, no matter what his circumstances are for hiding his identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change the fact that he's of a suspicious lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I only accepted the match because you're so intent on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When would you like to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you can play, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait until I get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this is quite different from holding the stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The fourth game of the Jyudan Match is next Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rest for a day after that. What about the following Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't affect my important fifth game of the Jyudan Match, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't wish for a nonchalant game like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... please play seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want you to say that you weren't playing seriously, when you lose, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I? Lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,IF! If!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind quitting the pros if I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't, everyone in the Go world would be shocked if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to seriously think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that I might lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. If I lose to that friend of yours, I will retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Retire...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will play in one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The match will start at ten, with three hours time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will refuse any visitors on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that I will play the match you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now be quiet, you're in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we will continue the problem from last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you figured out the answer to the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is B, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if white makes an eye here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you can play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,White will capture three stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can play a snap-back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if white comes here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,black can connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This becomes a deficient eye, so white only has this one eye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case white dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were able to solve this problem without a hint,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you're probably a higher-kyu player.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.37,Note,,0,0,0,,To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn your computer on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Kouyou is playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching! Since about half an hour ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real Touya Kouyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What flawless and efficient play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the one playing can see these possibilities.
